      <title>台北地震损坏建筑物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/earthquake-damages-buildings-in-taipei-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾遭受了四分之一世纪以来最强烈的地震，地震摧毁了台湾东部的数十座建筑物。超过50人受伤，部分芯片生产线中断。阿德里安·肯尼迪报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/earthquake-damages-buildings-in-taipei-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 03:22:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
