      <title>亚洲顶级 ECM 承销商在台湾和韩国开展更多活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/top-asia-ecm-underwriter-sees-more-activity-from-taiwan-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年亚太地区最大的股权交易安排机构花旗集团表示，更多台湾芯片、半导体公司及其持有人本季度寻求通过股票销售筹集资金。预计韩国和印度的活动也会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/top-asia-ecm-underwriter-sees-more-activity-from-taiwan-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 03:13:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
